;&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>2.假如我不再对任何事,任何人付出真心,或许我真的就不会再感到痛苦。&nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>3.友谊的悲哀莫过于,你把一个人当成你最好的朋友,但她并没有像你一样把当你成她最好</strong></font></span><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>的朋友!</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>4.一个人太相信自己,或是太相信/依赖某个人,把自己的喜怒哀乐全都一股脑寄托在他们身上,最后伤及你的人往往就是你认为最相信/看重/依赖/放不下/在乎的人或是事。 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>5.朋友是一种感觉,有些人相处几十年也不会成为朋友,有些人只要一见面就知道会是朋友。&nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>&nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>6.世上没有不伤人心的感情,或多或少,或大或小,它都会在你的灵魂上留下伤痕的,以伤痕为代价换得感情的喜悦,以感情的喜悦作为回报的伤痕。 &nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: no