uto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>9.若你流泪,湿的总是我的脸,若你悲戚,苦的总是我的心。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>10.乍临人生,你在哭,爱你的人在笑;生命终结,你在笑,爱你的人在哭。 &nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;><span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(195, 214, 155);&quot;><font color=&quot;#546d8e&quot; face=&quot;Arial&quot;><strong>11.无论一个朋友对你有多好,总有一天他做的某件事会让你伤心,而到时你应该学会原谅。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></font></span></p><p style=&quot;font: 16px/normal sans-serif; margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-s